title: Supply of creamery butter in Canada 2018
summary: The graph shows the Supply of creamery butter Canada in Tonnes Canada during 2018 .
The values are steady for the first three months and peak in April .
The Supply amount generally declines after April except for a significant surge in October and a slight increase in December .
gold: The data presented in the graph shows the supply of creamery butter in Canada over the year of 2018 in tonnes . The lowest supply of creamery butter can be observed in January . The supply increases constantly over the next months and reaches its highest value in June , after which it decreases with a similar rate and reaches a local minimum in September .
